# -------------------------
# Fonts / large binaries
# If you want to exclude large source font files (TTF/OTF) from public,
# add a rule here. Currently we keep web fonts (WOFF2) tracked in public/.
# Example (commented):
# assets/fonts/**/*.ttf
# assets/fonts/**/*.otf

# -------------------------
# Static site output
# We intentionally track public/ in this repo, so do NOT ignore it.
# If you later switch to building in CI and not committing public/, uncomment:
# public/

# End of file
